&lt;p&gt;Welcome to Day 2 of &lt;a href="/posts/2015/Aug/01/31-days-of-kindness-day-1-2015-edition.html" target="_blank"&gt;#31DaysOfKindness&lt;/a&gt;, 2015 edition! In today&amp;rsquo;s episode, I&amp;rsquo;m helping to make the world a cleaner place. No, I&amp;rsquo;m not going to stop talking&amp;hellip;&amp;nbsp;:)&lt;/p&gt;
</summary><category term="kindness"></category><category term="charity"></category><category term="fun"></category><category term="community"></category></entry><entry><title>31 Days of Kindness (Day 1) - 2015 Edition</title><link href="http://larry.wapnitsky.com/posts/2015/Aug/01/31-days-of-kindness-day-1-2015-edition.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2015-08-01T00:00:00-04:00</updated><author><name>Larry G. Wapnitsky</name></author><id>tag:larry.wapnitsky.com,2015-08-01:posts/2015/Aug/01/31-days-of-kindness-day-1-2015-edition.html</id><summary type="html">

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Block_31DaysLogo" src="/images/news/31DaysOfKindness2015/31-Days-of-Kindness.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As you may have read in the &lt;a href="/posts/2015/Jul/30/31-days-of-kindness-2015-edition.html" target="_blank"&gt;prior installment&lt;/a&gt;, I&amp;rsquo;m participating in &lt;strong&gt;#31DaysOfKindness&lt;/strong&gt; as part of not only improving myself, but helping out others. What was today&amp;rsquo;s mission?  A hand-written thank you note\letter to&amp;nbsp;someone.&lt;/p&gt;
</summary><category term="kindness"></category><category term="charity"></category><category term="fun"></category><category term="community"></category></entry><entry><title>31 Days of Kindness - 2015 Edition</title><link href="http://larry.wapnitsky.com/posts/2015/Jul/30/31-days-of-kindness-2015-edition.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2015-07-30T00:00:00-04:00</updated><author><name>Larry G. Wapnitsky</name></author><id>tag:larry.wapnitsky.com,2015-07-30:posts/2015/Jul/30/31-days-of-kindness-2015-edition.html</id><summary type="html">

